“TBT” 2009, this was my 1st year in Network Marketing. I didn’t have a clue what I was doing or what I was getting into. When I started Ardyss International, I was a girl from Miami who only knew the street life… from being a stripper, going to jail from trafficking drugs, being a victim of a horrible home invasion,and being shot multiple times. I wanted change so bad!! 

I tried so many things, but I only knew what I was familiar with. So I stepped out on faith and signed up for $250 to sell girdles and juice. That’s when the the “SHIFT HAPPENED “ not knowing that I was signing up for the most impactful experience of my life. I didn’t know that $250 was going to ultimately change my life and most importantly my mindset. I nurtured and sharpened a skill that I didn’t know I possessed which “No Man” can take from me 💯 

I met so many amazing women and men that influenced my life in so many ways - “Priceless”. This picture is where it all started. Truth be told, I really just wanted to dress like a Business Woman 😂 but I’m sharing all of this because I really want to encourage somebody this morning. The road may be unfamiliar, it may seem unfair, people will say it’s not going to work, you will feel unsupported or even attacked at times, you may feel like a fish out of water and so on. I felt and experienced all of the above, but I DID IT SCARED because I wanted change!! Look what God, sacrifice, and determination did for me. Listennnnn!! He will do it for YOU ❤️
